# CODEOWNERS - GitHub Authorization & Access Control
#
# This file specifies who must review code changes.
# GitHub automatically requests reviews from code owners.
#
# Syntax:
# path/to/file @username
# path/to/dir/ @username
#

# ============================================================
# DEFAULT OWNERS
# ============================================================

# All files default to maintainer
* @sharazsony

