# DOCUMENTATION
# ============================================================

# README must be reviewed by maintainer
/README.md @sharazsony

# All documentation changes require maintainer review
/docs/ @sharazsony
/docs/** @sharazsony

# Contributing guidelines
/CONTRIBUTING.md @sharazsony

# ============================================================
# CONFIGURATION & SETUP
# ============================================================

# Critical configuration files
