/LICENSE @sharazsony
/.github/ @sharazsony
/.github/CODEOWNERS @sharazsony

# ============================================================
# SCRIPTS
# ============================================================

# All automation scripts require review
/scripts/ @sharazsony
/scripts/** @sharazsony

